<h3>Motto</h3>
<p>Power to empower</p>
<h3>Benefits:</h3>
<ol>
<li>Govt to Govt - inter-govt communication, info sharing (potential - criminal record/jurisdiction issue)</li>
<li>Govt to Business: Single form - EoDB</li>
<li>Govt to citizen - Digilocker, Arogya Setu</li>
<li>Tele-medicine; Tele-Law</li></ol>
<h3>Challenges:</h3>
<ol>
<li>Digital Illiteracy - penetration rate faster than literacy rate</li>
<li>Infrastructure - rural areas - negligible connectivity</li>
<li>Cybercrime - Banking scam, Piracy</li>
<li>Security:
<ol>
<li>Internal - Fake news/propaganda; incite to riot; communal tension</li>
<li>External - China threat: Expert says only 8 min needed to shutdown India's critical Infra; Apps banned&nbsp;</li></ol></li>
<li>Women: Morphed images/sexual assault/rape threats</li>
<li>Children: Cyber bullying; indulging in illegal content (porn) and/or drugs (Silkroute - dark net)</li></ol>
<p>https://youtu.be/i1iemFpJGy0?t=623</p>
